{
  "stem": "15393.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I thought, I'll sit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "At least I was inside something, not outside freezing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I'll wait and when the tram starts, I'll go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We'll see what happens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Maybe I'll manage, maybe I won't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So there I was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then slowly, slowly, people started appearing and taking the tram.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "First workman, workers, men-- mostly men-- non-Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Of course, this was on the Aryan side, on the other side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they were boarding this tram, obviously, for the first tram to take them to work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So it must have been six o'clock in the morning or 5:30 or something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I put myself in sort of a little corner and squeezed myself there and there I sat in my attire.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "People were coming in, looking at me and looking the other way, leaning down.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The tram filled out almost to capacity.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I remember it was so full.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It usually was in Poland that it was overfull, it was overflowing, they were hanging out on the outside, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the conductor comes in and the driver, the train driver.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The conductor walks in, takes money from everyone, and here am I.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you now, all these things are very well, but you don't envisage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, I did not think about it beforehand, how am I going to-- if I had thought about it, I might not have been able to do it.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because logically speaking, you-- you are a dead duck.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was impossible to get through all of that without being-- without being denounced or caught or whichever.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But here I was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The conductor didn't see me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He walked past, he didn't see me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All the people around, nobody saw me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were doing, they were talking, they were doing their own thing, reading the paper.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
